<br>
You might also want to try updating all of your device drivers and get the latest xp service pack if you haven't already done that.<br>
<br>
Also, next time you get the BSOD look for the stop code--it's a number that looks like 0x???????? where the ?s are hexadecimal digits.  Try doing a Google search for the stop code.<br>
<br>
